// - VisaRequirement — blueprint Section 14.8's description overlaps
//   structurally with `DocumentRequirement` (Section 14.7). `Document`,
//   `DocumentRequirement`, and `DocumentReview` were added by the later
//   Document Schema Foundation checkpoint (below); the VisaRequirement /
//   DocumentRequirement boundary is resolved there
